### Video Overlay - Percentage-Based Positioning (Working Example)
# Uses percentage-based positioning for responsive overlays
# This example uses a real 480x720 video with tested parameters
# For a 480x720 video, this translates to:
# - width = 176px (36.76% of 480)
# - x = 226px (47.06% of 480)
# - y = 498px (69.22% of 720)
# 
# The overlay image will be automatically scaled to the specified percentage width
# while maintaining its aspect ratio (height auto-calculated)
POST {{baseUrl}}/video/overlay
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "videoUrl": "https://media.crafto.app/enhanced-video/0d336dda-d3d5-4408-8056-fb1cfaa94c8e?dimension=480x720&size=3102852&vbr=1032609&abr=96599&type=Devotional&enhancedVideo=true",
  "overlays": [
    {
      "imageUrl": "https://cnd.storyowl.app/users/8kJDs_owMTSktoxBaMeco/1768502353482_1_pfp.png",
      "imagePercentageWidth": 36.76,
      "imagePercentageFromStart": 47.06,
      "imagePercentageFromTop": 69.22
    }
  ]
}

### Video Overlay - Circle Crop (Working Example)
# Crops the overlay image into a circle shape before applying to video
# Uses FFmpeg geq filter to create circular transparency programmatically
# The circle is created by setting alpha=0 for pixels outside the circle radius
# 
# For a 480x720 video with 36.76% width overlay:
# - width = 176px (36.76% of 480) - circular crop applied before scaling
# - x = 226px (47.06% of 480)
# - y = 498px (69.22% of 720)
POST {{baseUrl}}/video/overlay
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "videoUrl": "https://media.crafto.app/enhanced-video/0d336dda-d3d5-4408-8056-fb1cfaa94c8e?dimension=480x720&size=3102852&vbr=1032609&abr=96599&type=Devotional&enhancedVideo=true",
  "overlays": [
    {
      "imageUrl": "https://cnd.storyowl.app/users/8kJDs_owMTSktoxBaMeco/1768502353482_1_pfp.png",
      "imageShape": "CIRCLE",
      "imagePercentageWidth": 36.76,
      "imagePercentageFromStart": 47.06,
      "imagePercentageFromTop": 69.22
    }
  ]
}

### Video Overlay - Percentage-Based Positioning (Generic Example)
