### Delete User Account
# Deletes the current authenticated user and all associated data
# 
# This endpoint will explicitly delete:
# - All sessions
# - All accounts
# - User metadata
# - All notifications
# - All orders
# - The user record
# 
# Headers:
# - Cookie: Session cookies (if using cookie-based auth)
# - Authorization: Bearer <token> (if using JWT token)
# 
# Response (200 OK):
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "message": "User and all associated data deleted successfully"
# }
# 
# Response (401 Unauthorized):
# {
#   "error": "Unauthorized - no valid session"
# }
# 
# Response (404 Not Found):
# {
#   "error": "User not found"
# }
# 
# Response (500 Internal Server Error):
# {
#   "error": "Failed to delete user"
# }
# 
# Warning: This action is irreversible. All user data will be permanently deleted.
# 
# The phoneNumber can be provided either as:
# 1. Query parameter: ?phoneNumber=+919876543210
# 2. Request body: { "phoneNumber": "+919876543210" }
# 
# Phone number must be in E.164 format (e.g., +919876543210)

