### Get Application Configuration V2
# Fetches application configuration for the requesting app only
# Filters config by x-app-id (or x-app-identifier) header
# 
# Headers:
# - Cookie: Session cookies (if using cookie-based auth)
# - Authorization: Bearer <token> (if using JWT token)
# - X-App-ID: App identifier (required, e.g., "alertpay-android", "jamun-android")
#   Alternative header: X-App-Identifier (also supported)
# 
# Behavior:
# - If x-app-id is present and matches a known app → returns that app's config
# - If x-app-id is missing or unknown → returns 401 Unauthorized
# 
# Response (200 OK):
# {
#   "success": true,
#   "appId": "alertpay-android",
#   "config": {
#     // App-specific configuration data
#   }
# }
# 
# Response (401 Unauthorized):
# {
#   "error": "Unauthorized - no valid session" | 
#            "Invalid or disabled app identifier: <app-id>" |
#            "Configuration not found for app ID: <app-id>"
# }
# 
# Response (500 Internal Server Error):
# {
#   "error": "Failed to fetch config" | "Internal server error"
# }
GET {{baseUrl}}/config/v2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
X-App-ID: com.kiranaapps.app

### Get Application Configuration V2 - Local Development
GET {{localUrl}}/config/v2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
X-App-ID: alertpay-android

### Get Application Configuration V2 - Production
GET {{baseUrlProd}}/config/v2
Authorization: Bearer J2pkBto2dMNgEWTe7eO8D2I28MMReWih
X-App-ID: com.kiranaapps.app

### Get Application Configuration V2 - Sharekaro App
