Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
X-App-ID: jamun-android

### ===== EQUENCE SMS API (Direct) =====

### Send OTP via Equence pushsms API (Direct - no intermediary server)
# Calls https://api.equence.in/pushsms directly
#
# Environment Variables:
# EQUENCE_USERNAME=sm9_tr
# EQUENCE_PASSWORD=pfJY_05-
# EQUENCE_TMPL_ID=1707176553065211775
# EQUENCE_SENDER_ID=ALRTSN
#
# Phone: 10 digits or full number with country code (e.g., 918855866494)

### Send OTP via Equence pushsms (with appHash)
POST https://api.equence.in/pushsms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "sm9_tr",
  "password": "pfJY_05-",
  "to": "918855866494",
