### ===== CRAFTO/KRAFTO API =====

### Crafto Home Feed v1.7
# Fetches Crafto quotes from database with pagination
# Automatically migrates old Crafto URLs to new CDN URLs
# 
# Authentication: Required (via session cookies or Bearer token)
# 
# Query Parameters:
# - offset: Offset string in YYYYMMDDHH format (optional, e.g., "2026011920")
#   Represents IST timestamp for pagination cursor
#   If not provided, uses current time (returns latest content)
# - limit: Number of items per page (optional, default: 20, max: 100)
# - category: Category type filter (optional, e.g., "motivational", "funny")
#   Filter quotes by category type. Use /api/crafto/categories to get available categories
# 
# Offset Format:
# - YYYY: 4-digit year
# - MM: 2-digit month (01-12)
# - DD: 2-digit day (01-31)
# - HH: 2-digit hour (00-23) in IST timezone
# Example: "2026011920" = January 19, 2026, 8:00 PM IST
# 
# Response (200 OK):
# {
#   "filterText": "motivational" | null,  // Category name if filtered, null otherwise
#   "selectedFilterId": "motivational" | null,  // Category name if filtered, null otherwise
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "type": "QUOTE",
#       "data": {
#         ... quote data (format varies by quote type)
#       }
#     }
#   ],
#   "offset": "2026011918" | null,  // Next page offset, null if no more pages
#   "limit": 20,
#   "popup": null,
#   "isBuggyFeedAlertWhitelisted": false,
#   "configuration": {
#     "logImageLoadExceptionEvents": true,
#     "logImageLoadSuccessEvent": false,
#     "logVideoExceptionEvent": true,
#     "logVideoLoadSuccessEvent": false
#   }
# }
# 
# Response (400 Bad Request):
# {
#   "error": "Invalid offset format. Expected YYYYMMDDHH"
# }
# 
# Response (401 Unauthorized):
# {
#   "error": "Unauthorized - no valid session"
# }
# 
# Response (500 Internal Server Error):
# {
#   "error": "Internal server error"
# }
# 
# Notes:
# - Pagination uses time-based cursor (offset) instead of page numbers
# - Returns quotes where createdAt <= offset date, ordered by newest first
# - Automatically migrates old media.crafto.app URLs to new CDN
# - Fetches limit+1 items to determine if more pages exist
# - Next offset is calculated from last item's createdAt timestamp
# - Category filtering: Use the category parameter to filter by category type
#   Get available categories from /api/crafto/categories endpoint

### Crafto Home Feed - First Page (Latest Content)
GET {{baseUrl}}/crafto/home/v1.7
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crafto Home Feed - With Custom Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/crafto/home/v1.7?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crafto Home Feed - With Offset (Pagination)
# Use the offset value returned from previous response
GET {{baseUrl}}/crafto/home/v1.7?offset=2026011920&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crafto Home Feed - Filter by Category
# Filter quotes by a specific category type
# First, get available categories from /api/crafto/categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/crafto/home/v1.7?category=motivational&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crafto Home Feed - Filter by Category with Pagination
# Combine category filter with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/crafto/home/v1.7?category=funny&offset=2026011920&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crafto Home Feed - Maximum Items Per Page
GET {{baseUrl}}/crafto/home/v1.7?limit=100
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Crafto Home Feed - Production
GET {{baseUrlProd}}/crafto/home/v1.7?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Test Background Removal via URL (Next.js Proxy)
